Uthe icala libe selidluliselwa ophikweni lwamaphoyisa aphenya amacala odlame lomndeni, ukuvikelwa kwezingane namacala ocansi. UZwane uthe lo mlisa waboshwa wagcinwa ezitokisini kusaqhubeka icala laze laphela. Kuthiwa uphenyo lwamaphoyisa luveze ukuthi ingane idlwengulwe izikhawu ezithathu ezihlukene.